{"data":[{"date":"15:44 17/08","title":"L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong nh\u00f3m \"h\u00e0ng t\u1ed3n\" s\u1eafp b\u1ecb Liverpool thanh l\u00fd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/liverpool-sap-ban-ragnar-klavan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng di\u1ec5n ra, Ragnar Klavan s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Liverpool trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t n\u01a1i nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u01a1n.</h2><h2>Liverpool s\u1eafp b\u00e1n Ragnar Klavan<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Goal \u0111\u01b0a tin, Liverpool s\u1eafp b\u00e1n Ragnar Klavan cho Cagliari v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 2 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (2.5 tri\u1ec7u euro). Trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Estonia s\u1ebd bay sang Italia trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u1ebb ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t cu\u1ed9c ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ch\u1ed1t l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1edbi Cagliari.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool s\u1eafp b\u00e1n Ragnar Klavan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool s\u1eafp b\u00e1n Ragnar Klavan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/liverpool-sap-ban-ragnar-klavan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Liverpool s\u1eafp b\u00e1n Ragnar Klavan cho Cagliari.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nRagnar Klavan gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool n\u0103m 2016, ra s\u00e2n 53 tr\u1eadn sau hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. S\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Van Dijk, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Joe Gomez c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7 khi\u1ebfn HLV Jurgen Klopp kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u1ea7n Klavan n\u1eefa. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Jurgen Klopp c\u00f2n c\u00f3 hai trung v\u1ec7 kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Dejan Lovren v\u00e0 Joel Matip.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 b\u1edfi trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 32 tu\u1ed5i, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u1edf \u0111\u1ec9nh cao phong \u0111\u1ed9. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Newcastle \u0111\u00e3 ng\u1ecf \u00fd mu\u1ed1n mua Klavan nh\u01b0ng Jurgen Klopp kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i Premier League.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool thanh l\u00fd h\u00e0ng t\u1ed3n<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ragnar Klavan, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 ba c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c ra \u0111i l\u00e0 Danny Ward, Jon Flanagan v\u00e0 Emre Can. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, The Kop v\u1eabn c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong di\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i l\u00e0 Simon Mignolet, Lazar Markovic, Pedro Chirivella, Marko Grujic v\u00e0 Divock Origi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 chi h\u01a1n 170 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho b\u1ed1n t\u00e2n binh, l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong tay HLV Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u \u1edf c\u1ea3 ba tuy\u1ebfn. V\u00ec v\u1eady, Liverpool \u0111ang t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft ra \u0111i v\u1eeba thu v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed, v\u1eeba t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho HLV Jurgen Klopp trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League g\u1eb7p West Ham, Liverpool gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-0 \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng Premier League.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Liverpool m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-cai-ten-tiep-theo-roi-liverpool-o-he-2018-172-194419.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! C\u00e1i t\u00ean ti\u1ebfp theo r\u1eddi Liverpool \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-klopp-tu-choi-ban-hang-thai-cho-newcastle-172-194271.html\">HLV Klopp t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i cho Newcastle</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ghi-ban-phut-bu-gio-klavan-di-vao-lich-su-premier-league-172-176760.html\">Ghi b\u00e0n ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd, sao Liverpool \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed NHA</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-liverpool-to-salah-tron-tap-luyen-172-173564.html\">\u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ed1 Salah tr\u1ed1n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u1edf Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-liverpool-len-tieng-thach-thuc-sergio-aguero-172-156173.html\">Sao Liverpool l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Sergio Aguero</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klavan-su-canh-tranh-vi-tri-la-tot-cho-liverpool-172-139137.html\">Klavan: S\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t cho Liverpool</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)\u00a0</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2472","checkdouble":"194675"},{"date":"15:38 17/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 Indonesia vs U23 L\u00e0o 19h00 ng\u00e0y 17/8 (Asiad 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/u23-indonesia-vs-u23-lao-tran-dau-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Indonesia vs U23 L\u00e0o: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Indonesia vs Olympic L\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng A Asiad 2018 l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 17/8.</h2>(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Palestine khi\u1ebfn ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia r\u01a1i v\u00e0o th\u1ebf kh\u00f3 \u1edf b\u1ea3ng A m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng L\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay v\u00e0 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp l\u00e0 H\u1ed3ng K\u00f4ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i (20/8) th\u00ec m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi L\u00e0o kh\u00e1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00ec \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean U23 L\u00e0o s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tinh th\u1ea7n tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i song so s\u00e1nh v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t th\u00ec \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n x\u1ee9 Tri\u1ec7u Voi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1eeda t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi U23 Indonesia quy\u1ebft th\u1eafng. U23 L\u00e0o ch\u1ec9 th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong hi\u1ec7p 1. Sang hi\u1ec7p 2, h\u1ecd hay b\u1ecb xu\u1ed1ng s\u1ee9c d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn c\u00e1c b\u00e0n thua l\u00e3ng x\u1eb9t.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Indonesia vs U23 L\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Asiad 2018 h\u00f4m nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Indonesia vs U23 L\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Asiad 2018 h\u00f4m nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/nhan-dinh-u23-indonesia-vs-u23-lao-19h-ngay-178-asiad-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">U23 Indonesia vs U23 L\u00e0o</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nU23 Indonesia c\u00f3 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 bi\u1ebft khai th\u00e1c hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t chi ti\u1ebft: Indonesia lu\u00f4n \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ef1c hay v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1eafng theo ki\u1ec3u h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t m\u1ed7i khi g\u1eb7p c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u01a1. <br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2471","checkdouble":"194676"},{"date":"15:41 17/08","title":"Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 ra h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/truong-doan-olympic-viet-nam-danh-gia-cau-thu-nhat-non-kinh-nghiem.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, HLV Park Hang Seo cho bi\u1ebft s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft th\u1eafng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 ngay \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.\r\n\r\n</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/hlv-park-hang-seo-tu-tin-o-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV\u00a0Park Hang Seo kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 mu\u1ed1n g\u1eb7p Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng D t\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn th\u01b0 h\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.\u00a0</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng n\u00f3i: <em>\"T\u00f4i v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1ecdt \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng 1/8 ASIAD 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn xa h\u01a1n n\u1eefa khi c\u00f9ng Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n tranh ch\u1ea5p ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D. T\u1eeb l\u00fac n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ph\u00e2n t\u00edch k\u0129 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ed1i \u01b0u nh\u1ea5t\".</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edf d\u0129 HLV Park Hang-seo v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D l\u00e0 b\u1edfi v\u00ec h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n n\u00e9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng E l\u00e0 Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang-seo \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf b\u1ea3ng E.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng Park n\u00f3i th\u00eam: <em>\"H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng E. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh h\u1ecd. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n s\u1edbm g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi h\u1ecd \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n hay b\u1ea5t k\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o c\u0169ng th\u1ebf, \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n tr\u00e1nh ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y. V\u00ec v\u1eady m\u00e0 tr\u1eadn Vi\u1ec7t Nam - Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd c\u0103ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft\".</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\"T\u00f4i \u0111ang l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u01b0ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00e0 qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00f4i. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng l\u00e0m h\u1ebft tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam\",</em> v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8 t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truong-doan-olympic-viet-nam-danh-gia-cau-thu-nhat-non-kinh-nghiem-168-194677.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/truong-doan-olympic-viet-nam-danh-gia-cau-thu-nhat-non-kinh-nghiem.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truong-doan-olympic-viet-nam-danh-gia-cau-thu-nhat-non-kinh-nghiem-168-194677.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 ra h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng trong n\u01b0\u1edbc, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u00f4ng D\u01b0\u01a1ng V\u0169 L\u00e2m \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt c\u00f2n \u00edt kinh nghi\u1ec7m chinh chi\u1ebfn.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/tien-ve-quang-hai-tu-tin-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban-292-194674.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/tien-ve-quang-hai-tu-tin-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/tien-ve-quang-hai-tu-tin-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban-292-194674.html\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Quang H\u1ea3i t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Quang H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 tin cho bi\u1ebft c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-quoc-dung-ve-phia-viet-nam-o-tran-gap-nhat-ban-168-194671.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/bao-han-quoc-dung-ve-phia-viet-nam-o-tran-gap-nhat-ban.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-quoc-dung-ve-phia-viet-nam-o-tran-gap-nhat-ban-168-194671.html\">B\u00e1o H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span><br>\r\nGi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea1m m\u1eb7t H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2470","checkdouble":"194677"},{"date":"15:44 17/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 Malaysia vs U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 19h00 ng\u00e0y 17/8 (Asiad 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/u23-malaysia-vs-u23-han-quoc-tran-dau-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Malaysia vs U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Malaysia vs Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c b\u1ea3ng E Asiad 2018 l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 17/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<br>\r\nU23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111ang l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f4ng cu\u1ed9c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5m HCV m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng khi \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p U23 Bahrain t\u1edbi 6-0 d\u00f9 ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ed1 1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Son Heung Min.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHwang Ui-jo l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi hattrick. Na Sang Ho c\u0169ng c\u00f3 2 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 2 b\u00e0n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Kim Jin Ya v\u00e0 Hwang Hee Chan. L\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \"Ronaldo x\u1ee9 H\u00e0n\" v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb b\u1edfi U23 Malaysia th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n U23 Bahrain n\u00ean U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c th\u1eeba kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Tottenham.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Malaysia vs U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Asiad 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Malaysia vs U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Asiad 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/nhan-dinh-u23-malaysia-vs-u23-han-quoc-19h00-ngay-178-asiad-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">U23 Malaysia vs U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e1ng quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd th\u1eafng U23 Malaysia v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t bao nhi\u00eau m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.\u00a0 U23 Malaysia c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Asiad 2018 nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eb3ng ai d\u00e1m tin v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a U23 Malaysia tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. M\u1ed1i th\u00f9 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 ASIAD 2014 (t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i ch\u00ednh H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c) c\u1ee7a U23 Malaysia kh\u00f3 m\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f2i.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2469","checkdouble":"194678"},{"date":"16:22 17/08","title":"B\u00e1o Th\u00e1i Lan khen Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, ch\u00ea \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 t\u01a1i t\u1ea3","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/bao-thai-lan-khen-olympic-viet-nam-che-doi-nha-toi-ta.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u00e1o Th\u00e1i Lan khen Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i s\u1edbm t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</h2><h2>B\u00e1o Th\u00e1i Lan khen Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau hai tr\u1eadn \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1edbi 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u00e1ng gi\u1ec1ng Th\u00e1i Lan ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed su\u00fdt thua \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 Bangladesh.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bao Thai Lan khen Olympic Viet Nam sau man trinh dien khong tot cua doi tuyen nuoc nay.\" title=\"B\u00e1o Th\u00e1i Lan khen Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/bao-thai-lan-khen-olympic-viet-nam-che-doi-nha-toi-ta.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>B\u00e1o Th\u00e1i Lan khen Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh t\u00edch tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00f3, b\u00e1o Th\u00e1i Lan khen Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ch\u00ea \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. T\u1edd Khaosod vi\u1ebft: &quot;L\u1ee9a U23 Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111ang ch\u1eefng l\u1ea1i sau khi \u0111o\u1ea1t HCV SEA Games 29, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed th\u1ee5t l\u00f9i so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 t\u1eebng ng\u00e0y, U23 Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111ang thua k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u00e1ng gi\u1ec1ng. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Worrawoot ch\u01b0a th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn n\u00e0o qua hai tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, c\u00f2n Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u00f9 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Pakistan v\u00e0 Nepal&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan b\u1ecb ch\u00ea t\u01a1i t\u1ea3<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111ang b\u1ecb thu h\u1eb9p khi h\u1ecd m\u1edbi gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m, ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Olympic Uzbekistan \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i. N\u1ebfu thua tr\u1eadn, Th\u00e1i Lan nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i trong vi\u1ec7c so th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t qu\u00e1 ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n&quot; l\u00e0 d\u00f2ng ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ec1 tr\u00ean SiamSport. T\u1edd n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfc l\u1eddi ch\u00ea th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Worrawoot: &quot;L\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan qu\u00e1 c\u1ea7u to\u00e0n, thi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o. Bangladesh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u01b0ng HLV Worrawoot ch\u1eb3ng th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ed3n \u00e9p \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;S\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7 quan c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua. N\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfn xa, \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng khi Chenrop Samphaodi \u0111ang sa s\u00fat phong \u0111\u1ed9&quot;.<br />\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018:</h2>\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truong-doan-olympic-viet-nam-danh-gia-cau-thu-nhat-non-kinh-nghiem-168-194677.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 ra h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-lang-tranh-truyen-thong-que-nha-sau-tran-thang-nepal-168-194673.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo l\u1ea3ng tr\u00e1nh truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Nepal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-quoc-dung-ve-phia-viet-nam-o-tran-gap-nhat-ban-168-194671.html\">B\u00e1o H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/bat-dong-noi-bo-olympic-nepal-da-tu-thua-viet-nam-ngay-truoc-tran-472-194637.html\">B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9, Olympic Nepal \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 thua Vi\u1ec7t Nam ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-gap-nhat-ban-khi-chien-thang-khong-con-qua-xa-xi-168-194634.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: Khi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 xa x\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-dung-tinh-toan-nhieu-o-tran-gap-nhat-ban-168-194633.html\">&ldquo;Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1eebng t\u00ednh to\u00e1n nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2468","checkdouble":"194680"},{"date":"16:10 17/08","title":"HLV Park Hang Seo n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/hlv-park-hang-seo-noi-gi-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, HLV Park Hang Seo cho bi\u1ebft s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft th\u1eafng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 ngay \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.\r\n\r\n</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/hlv-park-hang-seo-tu-tin-o-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV\u00a0Park Hang Seo kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 mu\u1ed1n g\u1eb7p Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng D t\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn th\u01b0 h\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.\u00a0</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng n\u00f3i: <em>\"T\u00f4i v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1ecdt \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng 1/8 ASIAD 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn xa h\u01a1n n\u1eefa khi c\u00f9ng Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n tranh ch\u1ea5p ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D. T\u1eeb l\u00fac n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ph\u00e2n t\u00edch k\u0129 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ed1i \u01b0u nh\u1ea5t\".</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edf d\u0129 HLV Park Hang-seo v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D l\u00e0 b\u1edfi v\u00ec h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n n\u00e9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng E l\u00e0 Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang-seo \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf b\u1ea3ng E.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng Park n\u00f3i th\u00eam: <em>\"H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng E. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh h\u1ecd. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n s\u1edbm g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi h\u1ecd \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n hay b\u1ea5t k\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o c\u0169ng th\u1ebf, \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n tr\u00e1nh ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y. V\u00ec v\u1eady m\u00e0 tr\u1eadn Vi\u1ec7t Nam - Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd c\u0103ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft\".</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\"T\u00f4i \u0111ang l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u01b0ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00e0 qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00f4i. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng l\u00e0m h\u1ebft tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam\",</em> v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8 t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truong-doan-olympic-viet-nam-danh-gia-cau-thu-nhat-non-kinh-nghiem-168-194677.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/truong-doan-olympic-viet-nam-danh-gia-cau-thu-nhat-non-kinh-nghiem.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truong-doan-olympic-viet-nam-danh-gia-cau-thu-nhat-non-kinh-nghiem-168-194677.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 ra h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng trong n\u01b0\u1edbc, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u00f4ng D\u01b0\u01a1ng V\u0169 L\u00e2m \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt c\u00f2n \u00edt kinh nghi\u1ec7m chinh chi\u1ebfn.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/tien-ve-quang-hai-tu-tin-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban-292-194674.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/tien-ve-quang-hai-tu-tin-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/tien-ve-quang-hai-tu-tin-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban-292-194674.html\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Quang H\u1ea3i t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Quang H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 tin cho bi\u1ebft c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-quoc-dung-ve-phia-viet-nam-o-tran-gap-nhat-ban-168-194671.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/bao-han-quoc-dung-ve-phia-viet-nam-o-tran-gap-nhat-ban.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-quoc-dung-ve-phia-viet-nam-o-tran-gap-nhat-ban-168-194671.html\">B\u00e1o H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span><br>\r\nGi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea1m m\u1eb7t H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2467","checkdouble":"194684"},{"date":"17:11 17/08","title":"Th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Nepal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/van-quyet-the-hien-su-tiec-nuoi-sau-tran-thang-nepal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nepal, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nepal.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Paksitan, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm Nepal m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f2i l\u1ea1i ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean trong su\u1ed1t 90 ph\u00fat t\u1ea1i Wibawa Mukti t\u1ed1i qua, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, qua \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt do h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 fair-play.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm Nepal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm Nepal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/video-ban-thang-van-quyet-olympic-viet-nam-20-olympic-pakistan.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft t\u1ecf r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm Nepal</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i m\u1edbi ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e9 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf v\u00f2ng sau. M\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Nepal, khi \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u00e0 s\u1ebd ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 nu\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nepal. Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cTo\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 so \u0111\u1ecd hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Nepal ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu. R\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc v\u00ec Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u01a1n hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi h\u1ecd \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i\u201d.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 ra nh\u01b0ng V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u1eabn nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh\u00a0 anh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 mang l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m vui cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9: \u201cOlympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u1ef9 cho m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u00ean t\u00f4i xin c\u1ea3m \u01a1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e3 sang t\u1eadn Indonesia c\u1ed5 v\u0169 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh. To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t c\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ed9ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i vui v\u00ec \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f3 ch\u01a1i Nepal, mang l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m vui cho m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi\u201d.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8 t\u1edbi.\u00a0\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/quang-hai-duoc-menh-danh-la-messi-viet-nam-o-asiad-168-194685.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/quang-hai-duoc-menh-danh-la-messi-viet-nam-o-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/quang-hai-duoc-menh-danh-la-messi-viet-nam-o-asiad-168-194685.html\">Quang H\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 Messi Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf ASIAD</span><br>\r\nM\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y gi\u00fap Quang H\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1eb7t cho c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00e1 m\u0129 mi\u1ec1u l\u00e0 Messi Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-noi-gi-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban-168-194684.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/hlv-park-hang-seo-noi-gi-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-noi-gi-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban-168-194684.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n?</span><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, HLV Park Hang Seo cho bi\u1ebft s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft th\u1eafng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 ngay \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 s\u1eafp...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/bao-thai-lan-khen-olympic-viet-nam-che-doi-nha-toi-ta-292-194680.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/bao-thai-lan-khen-olympic-viet-nam-che-doi-nha-toi-ta.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/bao-thai-lan-khen-olympic-viet-nam-che-doi-nha-toi-ta-292-194680.html\">B\u00e1o Th\u00e1i Lan khen Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, ch\u00ea \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 t\u01a1i t\u1ea3</span><br>\r\nB\u00e1o Th\u00e1i Lan khen Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i s\u1edbm t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truong-doan-olympic-viet-nam-danh-gia-cau-thu-nhat-non-kinh-nghiem-168-194677.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/truong-doan-olympic-viet-nam-danh-gia-cau-thu-nhat-non-kinh-nghiem.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truong-doan-olympic-viet-nam-danh-gia-cau-thu-nhat-non-kinh-nghiem-168-194677.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 ra h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng trong n\u01b0\u1edbc, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u00f4ng D\u01b0\u01a1ng V\u0169 L\u00e2m \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt c\u00f2n \u00edt kinh nghi\u1ec7m chinh chi\u1ebfn.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2466","checkdouble":"194686"},{"date":"17:27 17/08","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! \u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1i \u01b0u c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/day-doi-hinh-toi-uu-cua-chelsea-o-tran-gap-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Arsenal trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Sarri tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Stamford Bridge. C\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua th\u00f4ng tin l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn derby London.</h2><h2>T\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t ca ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng lo ng\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Cesc Fabregas. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Arsenal \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n giao h\u1eefu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nFabregas kh\u00f3 k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169. Anh g\u1eb7p kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh v\u1edbi Man City v\u00e0 c\u0169ng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n c\u1ee7a The Blues \u1edf Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Arsenal \u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1i \u01b0u c\u1ee7a The Blues h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Arsenal \u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1i \u01b0u c\u1ee7a The Blues h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/172219-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t ca ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Fabregas</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTiemoue Bakayoko \u0111\u00e3 r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp AC Milan theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. Trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hai b\u00ean k\u00fd k\u1ebft c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMateo Kovacic kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Huddersfield cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Nh\u01b0ng Kepa Arrizabalaga \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c sau khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Athletic Bilbao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMarco van Ginkel \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 sau giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u1edf PSV. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng ch\u1eef th\u1eadp v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay.\r\n<h2><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a Chelsea\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh Chelsea\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/3.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1i \u01b0u c\u1ee7a Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\nChelsea s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng 4-3-3 \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00e1 c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00ean ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nEden Hazard c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t sau khi ra s\u00e2n t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb h\u1ed3i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t sau khi l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAnh nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thay th\u1ebf Willian. Pedro \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Sarri trong v\u00e0i tu\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t giai \u0111o\u1ea1n ti\u1ec1n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea (4-3-3): Kepa &ndash; Azpilicueta, Luiz, Rudiger, Alonso &ndash; Kante, Jorginho, Barkley &ndash; Pedro, Morata, Hazard<br>\r\n<h2>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn</h2>\r\n- Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng 5 trong 6 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 thua Man City \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ra qu\u00e2n. H\u1ecd ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd thua 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1992<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Th\u1eddi c\u00f2n d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Napoli, HLV Sarri ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 4 trong s\u1ed1 57 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 (th\u1eafng 43, h\u00f2a 10)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Olivier Giroud \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n cho Arsenal khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 2/2017. N\u1ebfu ghi b\u00e0n cho Chelsea, anh s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 2 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n cho c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i sau Cesc Fabregas<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Aubameyang \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 150 trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p \u1edf 5 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c2u<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 CLB&nbsp;Chelsea:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-khen-ngoi-tan-binh-bom-tan-cua-chelsea-het-loi-172-194639.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i khen ng\u1ee3i t\u00e2n binh bom t\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a Chelsea h\u1ebft l\u1eddi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-chelsea-hlv-sarri-giua-hai-nga-barkley-kovacic-172-194552.html\">G\u00f3c Chelsea: Sarri gi\u1eefa hai ng\u1ea3 Kovacic - Barkley</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2465","checkdouble":"194687"},{"date":"17:45 17/08","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u00e0y c\u00e1ch gi\u00fap Morata l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u0103n b\u00e0n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/17/huyen-thoai-bay-cach-giup-morata-lay-lai-kha-nang-san-ban.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Dennis Wise tin r\u1eb1ng Morata c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 s\u0103n b\u00e0n nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 d\u1eabn c\u1ee7a Gianfranco Zola.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Morata m\u1edbi ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong n\u0103m 2018. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Chelsea sau khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh T\u00e2y Ban Nha tham d\u1ef1 World Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t m\u00e0 HLV Sarri mong mu\u1ed1n \u1edf m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o. \u0110\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 cho \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd, Morata v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u00e0y c\u00e1ch cho ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Morata l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u0103n b\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u00e0y c\u00e1ch cho ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Morata l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u0103n b\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/huyen-thoai-bay-cach-giup-morata-lay-lai-kha-nang-san-ban.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Dennis Wise cho r\u1eb1ng Zola c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Morata</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Dennis Wise cho r\u1eb1ng tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd Gianfranco Zola c\u1ee7a Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Morata gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 vi\u1ec7c gi\u00fap Morata ghi b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. \u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0i ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u01b0 mong \u0111\u1ee3i. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cM\u1ed9t khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o th\u1ef1c th\u1ee5 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi Premier League. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u1eady n\u00ean t\u00f4i k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n t\u1eeb Morata. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb Zola. S\u1ebd th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t n\u1ebfu Zola c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 che ch\u1edf Morata v\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. N\u1ebfu Morata ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, Chelsea s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh ti\u1ec1m t\u00e0ng h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i chia s\u1ebb g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng ghi b\u00e0n v\u1edbi Morata. Giroud ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u1ed5 s\u00fang khi c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xung quanh Morata ghi b\u00e0n c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i quan tr\u1ecdng. Ch\u00fang ta \u0111ang h\u01a1i thi\u1ebfu \u0111i \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nXu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2464","checkdouble":"194688"},{"date":"10:21 17/08","title":"Sao Man City ti\u1ebfn c\u1eed t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb thay th\u1ebf De Bruyne","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/sao-man-city-tien-cu-tai-nang-tre-thay-the-de-bruyne.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Kyle Walker kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 bi quan v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi Phil Foden v\u1eabn c\u00f2n hi\u1ec7n h\u1eefu n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0n anh h\u1ebft l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">De Bruyne ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/man-city-nhan-tin-cuc-soc-ve-de-bruyne-172-194571.html\" target=\"_blank\">Man City m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn c\u00fa s\u1ed1c</span> ngay \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i khi Kevin De Bruyne d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Theo d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t s\u00e2n Etihad n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i nghi thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eeb 2-3 th\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfp theo \u0111\u00e2y.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Phil Foden thay th\u1ebf De Bruyne ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng \u1edf Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Phil Foden thay th\u1ebf De Bruyne ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng \u1edf Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/sao-man-city-tien-cu-tai-nang-tre-thay-the-de-bruyne.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Phil Foden thay th\u1ebf De Bruyne ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng v\u00e0 ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n cho Man City?</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">Nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Premier League ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng v\u00ec v\u1eady m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111i t\u1eeb bi quan \u0111\u1ebfn ho\u1ea3ng lo\u1ea1n khi chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, Kyle Walker tin t\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0 Phil Foden c\u0169ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Man City.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">Phil Foden s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd?<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh: \u201cR\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Kevin l\u00e0 m\u1ea5t m\u00e1t l\u1edbn nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u01a1n c\u1eed nh\u01b0 Phil, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ea7u ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, lu\u00f4n lu\u00f4n l\u1eafng nghe, h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">\u201cT\u00f4i g\u1eb7p kh\u00f4ng \u00edt nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1ebb \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm t\u1ecf ra t\u1ef1 m\u00e3n nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 Phil, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5y l\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n cho \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t hay th\u1eadm ch\u00ed v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 17. Kh\u00f4ng, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn y\u00eau b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 mi\u1ec7t m\u00e0i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ee7 qu\u00ean tr\u00ean chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, ti\u1ec7c t\u00f9ng nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n b\u00e8 c\u00f9ng trang l\u1ee9a.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Man City s\u1ebd tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Huddersfield Town. \u1ede ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n Premier League 2018/19, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pep Guardiola \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf m\u00e0n chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c h\u01a1n b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh Arsenal ngay t\u1ea1i Emirates.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-da-bi-nguoi-cu-mikel-arteta-phan-boi-nhu-the-nao-172-194558.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/arsenal-da-bi-nguoi-cu-mikel-arteta-phan-boi-nhu-the-nao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-da-bi-nguoi-cu-mikel-arteta-phan-boi-nhu-the-nao-172-194558.html\">Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Mikel Arteta \u201cph\u1ea3n b\u1ed9i\u201d nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Pep Guardiola, ch\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 mang \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho Man City \u1edf...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">Gia Khoa (TTVN)</span></strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2463","checkdouble":"194652"},{"date":"11:01 17/08","title":"Emery gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft c\u01a1n kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i Arsenal nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/emery-giai-quyet-con-khung-hoang-canh-trai-arsenal-nhu-the-nao.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e2n binh Stephan Lichtsteiner \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00e1i k\u00e8o sang b\u00ean kia \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n khi \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 m\u1ea5t h\u1ebft nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">Arsenal kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i</span></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">N\u1ed7i bu\u1ed3n g\u1ea5p b\u1ed9i cho Arsenal trong tr\u1eadn thua t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n Premier League 2018/19, khi Ainsley Maitland-Niles s\u1edbm d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1eddi s\u00e2n v\u00e0 theo k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 ch\u1ea9n \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 y t\u1ebf Emirates, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng 20 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb trong v\u00f2ng hai th\u00e1ng t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Lichtsteiner c\u1ee7a Arsenal ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00e1i k\u00e8o v\u00ec kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Lichtsteiner c\u1ee7a Arsenal ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00e1i k\u00e8o v\u00ec kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/emery-giai-quyet-con-khung-hoang-canh-trai-arsenal-nhu-the-nao.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Lichtsteiner c\u1ee7a Arsenal s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00e1i k\u00e8o trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">Hung tin n\u00e0y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 khi\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1o Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh London h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o c\u01a1n kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc Maitland-Niles, c\u1ea3 Sead Kolasinac v\u00e0 Nacho Monreal c\u0169ng ng\u1ed3i ch\u01a1i x\u01a1i n\u01b0\u1edbc d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n v\u00ec l\u00fd do t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 chuy\u00ean ch\u00ednh cho \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">D\u00f9 sao, Unai Emery c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 ra ph\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u01b0\u1edbng gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n ngay \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua, khi Stephan Lichtsteiner v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay th\u1ebf Maitland-Niles tr\u00e1m \u0111\u00fang v\u00e0o vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00e0n em. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, t\u00e2n binh k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 v\u1ed1n s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u01a1i c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n, nh\u01b0ng anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i n\u00e0o v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha: \u201cCh\u1eb3ng ai mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ea3, nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n t\u00f4i c\u0169ng lu\u00f4n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng x\u1ea5u nh\u1ea5t. Maitland-Niles th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi r\u1eddi s\u00e2n, v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i c\u1ea3 Lichtsteiner c\u0169ng v\u1eady.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e1 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00e1i k\u00e8o. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00e0o s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Monreal \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111a d\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 h\u1eefu hi\u1ec7u r\u1ed3i.\u201d - Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Arsenal s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Chelsea trong tr\u1eadn derby th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 London.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-02-man-city-binh-moi-nhung-ruou-chua-moi-172-194363.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/arsenal-02-man-city-binh-moi-nhung-ruou-chua-moi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-02-man-city-binh-moi-nhung-ruou-chua-moi-172-194363.html\">Arsenal 0-2 Man City: B\u00ecnh m\u1edbi nh\u01b0ng r\u01b0\u1ee3u ch\u01b0a m\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City. V\u00e0 r\u00f5...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">Gia Khoa (TTVN)</span></strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\"> <o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2462","checkdouble":"194653"},{"date":"09:19 17/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Myanmar vs U23 Saudi Arabia 19h00 ng\u00e0y 17/8 (ASIAD 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/nhan-dinh-u23-myanmar-vs-u23-saudi-arabia-19h00-ngay-178-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Lorient vs Valenciennes l\u00fac 01h00 ng\u00e0y 18/8 (V\u00f2ng 4 gi\u1ea3i H\u1ea1ng 2 Ph\u00e1p Ligue 2 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Lorient vs Valenciennes 01h00 ng\u00e0y 188 H\u1ea1ng 2 Ph\u00e1p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Lorient vs Valenciennes 01h00 ng\u00e0y 188 H\u1ea1ng 2 Ph\u00e1p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/nhan-dinh-soi-keo-lorient-vs-valenciennes-giai-hang-2-phap-2018-19.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Lorient vs Valenciennes</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span>Lorient vs Valenciennes: 1-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>C\u1ea3 Lorient v\u00e0 Valenciennes \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i Ligue 2 2018/19 khi c\u00f9ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu 7 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 3 v\u00f2ng, ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 5 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi 2 l\u1ea7n, l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t x\u1ebfp \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed 3 v\u00e0 4 tr\u00ean\u00a0BXH<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSong Lorient thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, khi 4 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i t\u1ed5 \u1ea5m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, h\u1ecd th\u1eafng 2, h\u00f2a 1 v\u00e0 thua 1. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Valenciennes l\u1ea1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch khi b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong 5 tr\u1eadn xa nh\u00e0 g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y (th\u1eafng 3 v\u00e0 h\u00f2a 2).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nValenciennes l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u1ecf m\u00e0 l\u1ea1i kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00ean ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u1ecd c\u00e0ng h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n. Khi tinh th\u1ea7n tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i c\u00f9ng quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, Valenciennes c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. V\u1eady n\u00ean, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2461","checkdouble":"194654"},{"date":"09:26 17/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Sochaux vs Brest 01h00 ng\u00e0y 18/8 (H\u1ea1ng 2 Ph\u00e1p 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/nhan-dinh-sochaux-vs-brest-01h00-ngay-188-hang-2-phap-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Sochaux vs Brest l\u00fac 01h00 ng\u00e0y 18/8 (V\u00f2ng 4 gi\u1ea3i H\u1ea1ng 2 Ph\u00e1p Ligue 2 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Sochaux vs Brest 01h00 ng\u00e0y 188 H\u1ea1ng 2 Ph\u00e1p 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Sochaux vs Brest 01h00 ng\u00e0y 188 H\u1ea1ng 2 Ph\u00e1p 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/Sochaux-vs-Brest.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Sochaux vs Brest</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> Sochaux vs Brest</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>: 0-1</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\nSau 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a 2018/19 to\u00e0n thua, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Sochaux d\u1ea7n b\u1eaft nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-2 trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Ajaccio v\u00f2ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i n\u00e0y gi\u00fap Sochaux t\u1ea1m tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi nh\u00f3m b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 leo l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 13 tr\u00ean BXH.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Sochaux t\u1ea1i c\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n Ph\u00e1p, d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00ednh Brest, song Sochaux \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m, sau khi h\u00f2a 1-1 trong 120 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nG\u1eb7p nhau l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2 ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng 4 ng\u00e0y v\u00e0 Sochaux ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Sochaux s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u00f2i l\u1ea1i m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 v\u1eeba vay \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Brest \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch, khi b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 3 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t (th\u1eafng 2). Ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3, 3 l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Brest tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Sochaux \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n10 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, Sochaux th\u1eafng 3 tr\u1eadn, h\u00f2a 5 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 3 tr\u1eadn.<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2460","checkdouble":"194655"},{"date":"10:38 17/08","title":"Lionel Messi ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u1ed1i th\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Barca m\u00f9a t\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/lionel-messi-tiet-lo-muc-tieu-cua-barca-mua-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Lionel Messi ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Barca m\u00f9a n\u00e0y l\u00e0 ngai v\u00e0ng Champions League sau b\u1ed1n n\u0103m li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c.</h2><h2>M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Barca<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch La Liga m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0ng t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 Barcelona v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Real Madrid v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League ba l\u1ea7n li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Barca t\u1ecf ra v\u00f4 duy\u00ean \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c khi d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft trong b\u1ed1n m\u00f9a g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lionel Messi ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Barca m\u00f9a t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lionel Messi ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Barca m\u00f9a t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/lionel-messi-tiet-lo-muc-tieu-cua-barca-mua-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Lionel Messi ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Barca m\u00f9a n\u00e0y l\u00e0 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Barca d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c AS Roma. V\u00ec v\u1eady, Lionel Messi ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Barca m\u00f9a n\u00e0y l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League: \"M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch La Liga v\u00e0 C\u00fap nh\u00e0 vua\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf Champions League, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf c\u00e1i c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng knock out. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 mang chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap \u0111\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ebd v\u00e0 l\u00e2u \u0111\u1eddi n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ebfn Nou Camp\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>S\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Barca<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Barca \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam b\u1ed1n t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng g\u1ed3m Arthur Melo, Clement Lenglet, Arturo Vidal v\u00e0 Malcom. Nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u00f2n khuy\u1ebft thi\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edbi c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn Messi ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch h\u01a1n: \"M\u00f9a n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 m\u1ea1nh. Nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca m\u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi v\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u Si\u00eau C\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha 2018 sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Sevilla.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Barcelona m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-barcelona-thanh-minh-cho-phong-do-sa-sut-cua-luis-suarez-172-194570.html\">HLV Barcelona thanh minh cho phong \u0111\u1ed9 sa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Luis Suarez</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/mark-van-bommel-su-nghiep-chim-noi-cua-ga-tieu-phu-389-194547.html\">Mark Van Bommel: S\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p ch\u00ecm n\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a g\u00e3 ti\u1ec1u phu</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-se-khong-ban-pogba-cho-barca-172-194472.html\">MU s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Pogba cho Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/roma-chuan-bi-bao-thu-barca-thanh-cong-180-194430.html\">Roma chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u201cb\u00e1o th\u00f9\u201d Barca th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-muon-mua-rabiot-cua-psg-180-194389.html\">Real l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch cu\u1ed7m m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/giai-cuu-barcelona-du-bi-hang-sang-duoc-dam-bao-tuong-lai-180-194378.html\">Gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u Barcelona, d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb h\u1ea1ng sang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2459","checkdouble":"194656"},{"date":"09:31 17/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Lorient vs Valenciennes 01h00 ng\u00e0y 18/8 (H\u1ea1ng 2 Ph\u00e1p 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/nhan-dinh-lorient-vs-valenciennes-01h00-ngay-188-hang-2-phap-201819.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Lorient vs Valenciennes l\u00fac 01h00 ng\u00e0y 18/8 (V\u00f2ng 4 gi\u1ea3i H\u1ea1ng 2 Ph\u00e1p Ligue 2 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Lorient vs Valenciennes 01h00 ng\u00e0y 188 H\u1ea1ng 2 Ph\u00e1p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Lorient vs Valenciennes 01h00 ng\u00e0y 188 H\u1ea1ng 2 Ph\u00e1p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/nhan-dinh-soi-keo-lorient-vs-valenciennes-giai-hang-2-phap-2018-19.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Lorient vs Valenciennes</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span>Lorient vs Valenciennes: 1-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>C\u1ea3 Lorient v\u00e0 Valenciennes \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i Ligue 2 2018/19 khi c\u00f9ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu 7 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 3 v\u00f2ng, ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 5 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi 2 l\u1ea7n, l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t x\u1ebfp \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed 3 v\u00e0 4 tr\u00ean\u00a0BXH<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSong Lorient thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, khi 4 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i t\u1ed5 \u1ea5m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, h\u1ecd th\u1eafng 2, h\u00f2a 1 v\u00e0 thua 1. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Valenciennes l\u1ea1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch khi b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong 5 tr\u1eadn xa nh\u00e0 g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y (th\u1eafng 3 v\u00e0 h\u00f2a 2).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nValenciennes l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u1ecf m\u00e0 l\u1ea1i kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00ean ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u1ecd c\u00e0ng h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n. Khi tinh th\u1ea7n tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i c\u00f9ng quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, Valenciennes c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. V\u1eady n\u00ean, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2458","checkdouble":"194657"}]}